!! ---------------
!! To represent phonologic variations in word forms we use the following
!! symbols (archiphones) in the lexicon files:
%{АЯØ%}	!!= __@CODE@__
%{ЫИØ%}	!!= __@CODE@__
%{ЫØ%}	!!= __@CODE@__ +Loc
%{УЮØ%}	!!= __@CODE@__
